Limpieza de datos

In [4]:
NaNCount, PercMiss = [], []
nM = len(PeakTable)
for m in range(nM):
    Mi = DataTable.iloc[:,m+4]
    NaNCount.append(Mi.isna().sum())
    PercMiss.append(NaNCount[m]*100/len(DataTable))
    
del nM, m, Mi

PeakTable['PercMiss'] = PercMiss
PeakTableClean = PeakTable[PeakTable.PercMiss < 10]
print(PeakTableClean.shape)

(173, 4)

Splitting en conjuntos de Train & Test

In [5]:
X = DataTable[PeakTableClean['Name']]
Y = np.array([1 if outcome == 'INF' else 0 for outcome in DataTable['Class']])
print(X.shape)
print(Y.shape)
XTrain, XTest, YTrain, YTest, Ctrain, Ctest = train_test_split(X, Y, 
                                                               DataTable.Class,
                                                               test_size=0.2,
                                                               stratify=Y,
                                                               random_state=40)
print("Train = {} samples with {} positive cases.".format(len(YTrain),sum(YTrain)))
print("Test = {} samples with {} positive cases.".format(len(YTest),sum(YTest)))

Normalización y Escalado de Datos, e Imputación de valores missing

In [6]:
XTrainScale, mu, sigma = cb.utils.scale(np.log(XTrain), method='auto', return_mu_sigma=True)
XTrainKnn = cb.utils.knnimpute(XTrainScale, k=3)

XTestScale = cb.utils.scale(np.log(XTest), method='auto', mu=mu, sigma=sigma)
XTestKnn = cb.utils.knnimpute(XTestScale, k=3)

del mu, sigma

Optimización de Hiperparámetros por K-fold cross-validation

In [7]:
cv = cb.cross_val.KFold(model=cb.model.PLS_SIMPLS,
                        X=XTrainKnn,
                        Y=YTrain,
                        param_dict={'n_components': [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]},
                        folds=5,
                        n_mc=10)
cv.run()

Construcción del Modelo y Evaluación

In [10]:
model = cb.model.PLS_SIMPLS(n_components=2)
YPredTrain = model.train(XTrainKnn, YTrain)
YPredTest = model.test(XTestKnn)

EvalTrain = [YTrain, YPredTrain]
EvalTest = [YTest, YPredTest]

# Save Loadings & Feature Importance 
model_weights = model.x_weights_            # [LV1, LV2, ...]
model_fi = model.feature_importance_        # [VIP, Coefficient]

# Evaluate Model (include Test Dataset)
model.evaluate(testset=EvalTest,
               label=Ctrain,
               legend='all')

Bootstrap Resampling del Modelo

In [12]:
# Extract X Data and Train Model
XBoot = DataTable[PeakTableClean['Name']]
XBootLog = np.log(XBoot)
XBootScale = cb.utils.scale(XBootLog, method='auto')
XBootKnn = cb.utils.knnimpute(XBootScale, k=3)
YPredBoot = model.train(XBootKnn, Y)

# Build Boostrap Models
bootmodel = cb.bootstrap.BCA(model, bootnum=100) 
bootmodel.run()
